parameters:
\nc<Reporter>Hey, Saki-chan! Right on time. Come on, let's go quickly.
I've reserved a nice place.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Oh, thank you for inviting me today! But, is it really okay
for someone like me to join?

\nc<Reporter>Of course! You're the star this time, Saki-chan. The last
show was a huge success, and I'd even like to make a sequel.

\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>Ahaha, I'm looking forward to working with you next time
too. (Did I sound a bit like a businessman just now...?)
\nc<Staff>It's about time, so let's go quickly!

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>(Come to think of it, it feels a bit early... Is this what
they call a wholesome wrap party?)
